description:
This course is for beginner and intermediate level. This Course  contains practical and lab. Step by Step all things are explained with practical so students can use laptop/desktop and follow the steps. In end of each section there is quiz so students can check that they have understood concept or not. 

There is a lab with splunk forwarder-searchhead-indexer setup so student can use AWS ubuntu Vms or their own Vms/servers to do this lab.

There is a Project section and students can develop Web Analytic Splunk App in this project  section.

In last section there are 100+ interview questions.
title: Data Analytics Using Splunk - Hands On!
